  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_738f9a1ad45f5579a26041da2e57c0e2">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Scanned police interrogations relating to specific acts of terrorism in Indonesia  by Jemaah Islamiyah and other groups, including bombings in Bali, Abu Bakar Ba'asyir, the Poso detainees, the Mariott bombing, and the Austrialian embassy bombing.</p>  </scopecontent>
